Package: saternet
Version: 1.0.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8)
Maintainer: chintan patel
Description: Python virtual environment manager for Linux
 saternet is a clean, professional CLI tool for managing Python
 virtual environments on any Linux distribution. It provides
 environment listing, creation, activation helpers, scanning,
 and detailed inspection, all from a single command.
